The OGuild, or Open Guild, unites open practitioners (& those who want to work with them) to strengthen connection, identity/reputation, and branding as well as catalyze the flow of resources. As a cooperative, guild members are owners who retain their individuality and freedom while sharing access to services and gaining benefits that are usually only accessible to employees/executives of large corporations.

